<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:29">Did you know The Salvation Army is a Church?</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:95">
		Meeting human needs, in His name. If you're looking for a church to call home, or if you're just needing to hear the message of hope that can be found in the Gospel of Jesus Christ, we invite you to visit one of our church locations near you.
	</p>
